How We Measure Value
Our proven approach to self-funding does more to control costs and maximize your benefit plan dollars.












                Custom Solutions
            
Self-funded plans are not created from a plug-and-play formula. We take the time to address your cost and care needs and long-term goals with tailored coverage that's within budget.

Learn More












                Health Management
            
HPI provides a strategic framework that includes a wide range of evidence-based programs tailored to meet your needs. We analyze data trends and compare with national norms to develop impactful programs that strengthen your bottom line.

Learn More












                Benefit Administration
            
Our administrative services, commitment to leading edge technology, and proven performance work together to preserve your funds, maximize cash flow and ease overall plan management.

